      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Tenrō Clan <br />The benefits of your bloodline's transformation have natural altered your body. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>Increase your Strength or Constitution score by 1, to a max of 20.</li><li>While wearing no or light armor, you can use your Strength or Constitution modifier instead of Dexterity when calculating your armor class.</li><li>You reduce all incoming bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage by -3.</li></ul>",
